              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Objective: Conduct a comprehensive audit of all files within the \"Theeb Ecosystem\" vault. Your goal is to evaluate the logical flow, technical consistency, and strategic clarity of the entire knowledge base.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Tasks:",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Structural Audit: Analyze the hierarchy from 00-THDG-GROUP down to 06-THDG-Clinical-Ventures. Does the folder structure logically support the scaling of an \"Agent-Based AI Infrastructure\"? Identify any structural redundancies or \"orphan\" concepts.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Conceptual Consistency: Evaluate the core definitions (e.g., Clinical Intelligence Infrastructure, Agent-Based AI, Clinical Evidence Assistant). Ensure these terms are used consistently across all index files and sub-documents without contradiction.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Gap Analysis: Identify \"blind spots\" in the documentation. For example, is the transition from \"Diagnostic Reasoning\" to \"Revenue Cycle Management\" clearly defined, or is there a missing architectural layer?",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
                  "text": "Refinement & Clarity Roadmap: Provide a concrete plan to rewrite or restructure these files to make them \"investor-ready\" and \"developer-clear.\" Suggest a unified naming convention and a standardized template for all _INDEX files.",
                  "type": "text",
                  "version": 1
                }
              ],
              "direction": "ltr",
              "format": "",
              "indent": 0,
              "type": "paragraph",
              "version": 1,
              "textFormat": 0,
              "textStyle": ""
            },
            {
              "children": [
                {
                  "detail": 0,
                  "format": 0,
                  "mode": "normal",
                  "style": "",
