      "promptContent": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "\n\nThe Professional Audit & Alignment PromptRole: Act as a Senior Systems Architect and AI Strategy Consultant specializing in HealthTech and Clinical Intelligence Infrastructures.Objective: Conduct a comprehensive audit of all files within the \"Theeb Ecosystem\" vault. Your goal is to evaluate the logical flow, technical consistency, and strategic clarity of the entire knowledge base.Tasks:Structural Audit: Analyze the hierarchy from 00-THDG-GROUP down to 06-THDG-Clinical-Ventures. Does the folder structure logically support the scaling of an \"Agent-Based AI Infrastructure\"? Identify any structural redundancies or \"orphan\" concepts.Conceptual Consistency: Evaluate the core definitions (e.g., Clinical Intelligence Infrastructure, Agent-Based AI, Clinical Evidence Assistant). Ensure these terms are used consistently across all index files and sub-documents without contradiction.Gap Analysis: Identify \"blind spots\" in the documentation. For example, is the transition from \"Diagnostic Reasoning\" to \"Revenue Cycle Management\" clearly defined, or is there a missing architectural layer?Refinement & Clarity Roadmap: Provide a concrete plan to rewrite or restructure these files to make them \"investor-ready\" and \"developer-clear.\" Suggest a unified naming convention and a standardized template for all _INDEX files.Strategic Vision: Based on the current files, propose a \"Version 2.0\" vision for this ecosystem that enhances the synergy between the different ventures (like Dawali-Vascular and Union-Clinics).Output Format: Provide a structured report with:Current State Assessment (Critical Review)Inconsistency Report (List of contradictions or vague areas)Proposed Infrastructure Schema (Better folder/file organization)Refined \"Identity\" Statement (A polished, high-impact version of the CII mission).\n\n"
        }
